---
import Whisk from './illustrations/Whisk.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-ivory texture-paper overflow-hidden" data-section="about">
  <!-- Whisk decoration -->
  <div class="absolute top-16 right-12 opacity-20 hidden md:block">
    <Whisk size="w-10 h-20" class="tilt-right" />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <span class="text-label text-sage">02 — Our Craft</span>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-20">
    <!-- Left: Polaroid photos -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[40%] relative">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 pb-12 rounded-sm shadow-lg tilt-left inline-block">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517433367423-c7e5b0f35086?w=600&auto=format&q=80"
            alt="Baker's hands kneading dough on a flour-dusted wooden surface"
            class="w-64 h-72 object-cover rounded-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="text-script text-base text-caramel/60 mt-2 text-center">fresh every morning</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-4 md:right-8 bg-white p-3 pb-12 rounded-sm shadow-lg tilt-right inline-block">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486427944299-d1955d23e34d?w=400&auto=format&q=80"
            alt="Golden croissants cooling on a wire rack"
            class="w-40 h-48 object-cover rounded-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="text-script text-sm text-caramel/60 mt-2 text-center">butter & patience</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Editorial Copy -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[55%] md:ml-auto flex flex-col justify-center">
      <h2 class="text-display-lg text-cocoa mb-10 md:mb-16">Our Story</h2>

      <div class="max-w-xl space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-espresso/80">
          <span class="font-display text-6xl md:text-7xl italic float-left mr-3 mt-1 leading-[0.8] text-caramel font-bold">B</span>akes
          Bay was born from a simple belief — that every dessert should feel like an occasion. Nestled along the
          quiet stretch of Maruthamalai Road in Coimbatore, we set out to craft beverages and desserts that don't
          just satisfy a craving but create a moment worth remembering.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-espresso/60">
          From our signature Royal Falooda — a towering celebration of rose, vermicelli, and hand-churned ice
          cream — to our freshly muddled mojitos and creamy lassis, every item on our menu is made by hand,
          made fresh, and made with intention.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-3 border-caramel/40 pl-6 py-4 my-10">
          <p class="text-script text-2xl md:text-3xl text-cocoa leading-snug">
            "We don't just bake. We make the quiet moments between conversations a little sweeter."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-espresso/60">
          What started as a neighbourhood dessert bar has become Coimbatore's destination for those who
          believe that a well-made falooda is a form of art, and that the best conversations happen over
          something freshly baked.
        </p>

        <p class="text-script text-lg text-caramel mt-8">— The Bakes Bay Family</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
